data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
Foie gras served with toasted brioche and a glass of sweet wine.
It can also be quickly seared on a high heat as it is in Vineet Bhatia's spice seared foie gras, wild mushroom naan and fennel-mango chutney salad.

data.name: label3.Text
data.value:
The vegetables vary, the spices vary, the meat varies – it’s one of those many dishes that has crossed many borders and morphed along with way.
It has lamb, and millet as the grain, which holds up nicely in soups and stews, retaining its texture and shape well.
